      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Deseed the <strong>pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into rough chunks</p><p>Crush the <strong>garlic </strong>open by squashing it with the side of a knife and remove the skins</p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
